summary: I like working with both people and data. That's why I am a Clojure developer and a community manager. Currently I'm based in Amsterdam. Previously I've been living, studying and working in Eritrea, Sudan, China and 5 European countries. By education I am a Marine Spatial Planner but since moving to the Netherlands I transitioned to an IT career.
